Shearer Quits England National Squad
LONDON , November 15 ( Xinhua ) -- England captain Alan Shearer on Sunday pulled out of the squad for Wednesday night 's friendly against the Czech Republic at Wembley .
The 28-year-old Newcastle United striker damaged a hamstring during the first half of United 's 1 - 1 draw with Sheffield Wednesday at St James ' Park on Saturday .
A club spokesman said : " Alan has spoken to the England people and will not be traveling down for the game .
